#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:173
msgid ""
"On Windows, your IPv4 MTU value is measured by using IPv4 DF flag, IPv6 MTU "
"is minus 20 from this value. There is no easy way to measure IPv6 MTU "
"directly on Windows platform"
msgstr ""
"在Windows系统上，IPv4的MTU值通过IPv4 DF标记（DF flag）检测，IPv6的MTU值在此基"
"础上减去20。在Windows系统上没有简单的方法来直接检测IPv6的MTU值"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:15
msgid "Optimize MTU"
msgstr "优化MTU"

#: src/Frame/OptimizeMtu/OptimizeMtuFrame.cpp:171
msgid ""
"Optimize MTU function only meaningful if there is \"Path MTU Blackhole\" or "
"tinc can't perform IPv4 Path MTU Discovery automatically on your system"
msgstr ""
"优化MTU功能仅在存在“路径MTU黑洞（Path MTU Blackhole）”时，或是tinc无法在你的"
"系统上自动执行IPv4 路径MTU发现（Path MTU Discovery）时有意义"

